quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  4,15,"Ne bakholanga eshifwolo mubakhasi benyu, munyoole abaloli bane mwinywe, nibabalola, mubekalile munzu okhula shinga lifwa libabukula nohomba Nyasaye abererere injila yindi"
  4,16,"Ne babili mwinywe nibakhola (eshifwolo) ako mubasandie (mubahe eshinyasio) ne nibekanila mana baba abalayi mubaleshele. Toto Nyasaye ni Oweshileshelo muno, Owetsimbabaasi po"
  4,17,"Toto eshileshelo shifuchililwa nende Nyasaye ni shiabalia bakholanga amabii mubusilu, mana nibekanila nibasaba eshileshelo mulwangu. Abo nibo ba Nyasaye achamilanga eshileshelo shiabu. Ne Nyasaye ni Omumanyi muno Owamachesi po"
  4,18,"Ne babula eshileshelo balia bakholanga amabii, okhula mulala wabu niyolelwa nende lifwa, mana aboole: “Toto esie lano ndikanile.” Nohomba balia bafwitsanga nibali abakhayi. Abo khwabakasilia eshinyasio eshilulu"
  4,19,"Enywe abasuubila, shimuchamilwa okhuchelama(okhukalusia) abakhasi nende amaani tawe . Ne mulabasandia mbu khomubukule khubiamwabahelesia tawe, halali nibakhola obubii bwa habulafu. Ne mwikhale ninabo obulayi, ne nikali mbu bamusinya munyala okhukhaya eshindu na Nyasaye aramwo tsikhabi tsinyinji"
  4,20,"Ne nimwenya okhukalukhasia Omukhasi abundu womukhasi wundi, ne mulala khubo mwamuhelesiyia omwandu omunji, mulabukulakhwo khumwandu oko shiosi shiosi tawe. Ne nimubukula muba mukholele obubii ne ni eshionono shili habulafu"
  4,21,"Ne mwakhabukula murie nimumalile okhwinjilana enywe khwenywe, ne abakhasi abo babukula khwinywe indakano isiro"
  4,22,"Ne mulateshia Abakhasi babasenywe bateshia tawe, halali khu kalia kabura. Toto esho ni eshifwolo nende oshisinyo nende injila imbii"